Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.19,0:00:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.19,0:00:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.79,0:00:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在大家都静静睡下的夜晚\Nみんなが寝静まった夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从窗口眺望夜空的话\N窓から空を見ていると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.69,0:00:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以看到很厉害的东西\Nとっても　すごいものを　見たんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.59,0:00:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大人们都笑者说\N大人は誰も笑いながら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.59,0:00:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我电视看太多了\Nテレビの見過ぎと言うけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.29,0:00:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我绝对绝对\N僕は　絶対に絶対に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会说谎\N嘘なんか言ってない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.79,0:00:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,决不会用名为常识的眼镜\N常識と言う眼鏡で
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.19,0:00:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我们的世界\N僕たちの世界は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.59,0:00:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进行窥视\Nのぞけやしないのさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.59,0:00:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了梦想的\N夢を忘れた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.59,0:01:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古老的地球人啊\N古い地球人よ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.59,0:01:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇妙的感觉\N不思議な気持ち
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.93,0:01:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.13,0:01:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的\N本当のことさ

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.84,0:01:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从拉比安玫瑰来了一个叫做露·露卡的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.12,0:01:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望亚加玛快点从香格里拉出去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.94,0:01:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再在殖民卫星上开洞可就不得了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.13,0:01:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,努力去打开舱口我还是太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.84,0:01:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当老好人的少年可活不下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.73,0:01:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第八话 二度敲响镇魂的钟声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.15,0:02:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安眠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.74,0:02:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨克的勇士们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.90,0:02:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们多吃ㄧ些水果吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.09,0:02:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潘帕,你怎么可以死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.08,0:02:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N敲响使灵魂安息的钟声吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.29,0:02:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不去整装新型MS,办什么丧礼阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.32,0:02:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是在地球..什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.82,0:02:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道再地球\N死人都要办丧礼的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.91,0:02:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道哈曼大人替大家\N作天堂卫星还不够吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.22,0:02:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个计划阿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.91,0:02:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家希望有更温暖的\N人与人之间的交流阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.55,0:03:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在亚加玛想从另一边的舱口离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.46,0:03:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潘帕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.84,0:03:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们都忘记哈曼大人的话了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.17,0:03:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等战胜后再来凭吊死者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.00,0:03:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.70,0:03:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下,马士文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.35,0:03:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丧礼到此结束\N到安多拉号准备出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.67,0:03:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是丧礼还没结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.10,0:03:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是马士文大人的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.11,0:03:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打败亚加玛\N才是对死者最好的安慰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.40,0:03:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么你们还不懂吗?\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.89,0:04:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度,接到信号的话你会下来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.93,0:04:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.22,0:04:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.48,0:04:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是信号弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.39,0:04:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是是红色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.62,0:04:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.76,0:04:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是舱口打开的信号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.90,0:04:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舱口打开的信号是青色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.74,0:04:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那红色呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.79,0:04:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是收破烂业者的集合讯号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.54,0:04:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了遭了\N奇马达被
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.13,0:04:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收破烂业者抓起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.29,0:04:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?在舱口前面的广场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.54,0:04:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什么?当然是去就马奇达了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.98,0:04:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地的人真是废物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.50,0:04:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.69,0:04:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收破烂工会真的那么粗暴吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.00,0:04:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何止粗暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.36,0:04:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工会的家伙掌握舱口的开关权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.88,0:04:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿这个来赚取暴利呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.28,0:04:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样你知道事情的严重吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.29,0:04:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露卡怎么进来的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.04,0:05:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她要进来很简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.64,0:05:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,核战机比MS小多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.42,0:05:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布拉杜舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.42,0:05:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度开动Z高达了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.36,0:05:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么擅自出动?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.79,0:05:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他还很气愤舰长不在甲板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.26,0:05:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快阻止他!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.05,0:05:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不能\把香格里拉的命运交给其他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.39,0:05:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等露卡探完情况回来吧\N捷度你现在去太早了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.47,0:05:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们破铜烂铁工会\N必须团结奋发才可以!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.77,0:05:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人想为了外头来的人\N打开舱门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.17,0:05:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试问外面的船\N过去曾给我们带来好处吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.08,0:05:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.78,0:05:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的MS被他们破坏...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.28,0:05:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?你的MS怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.52,0:05:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了修好它\N我可是彻夜赶工做的阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.42,0:05:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会坏掉也是外头的人弄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.67,0:05:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们不能置之不理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.03,0:06:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露卡,她手脚真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.63,0:06:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有有人家产被他们夺走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.81,0:06:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得可恶吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.74,0:06:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.62,0:06:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.72,0:06:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要吃吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.00,0:06:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,我是素食者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.56,0:06:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你再做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.68,0:06:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么坏事也没做阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.23,0:06:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干什么?\N捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太没用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.65,0:06:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手!很危险的!会爆炸的,会爆炸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.39,0:06:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是炸弹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.40,0:06:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是强力炸弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.40,0:06:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别乱摸,不然可能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.11,0:07:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了,安静点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.38,0:07:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,点燃那个信号弹\N亚加玛就会飞起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.43,0:07:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是敌人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.44,0:07:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舱口还没打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.28,0:07:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扩大破铜烂铁堆\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.65,0:07:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是Z高达,不会错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.93,0:07:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要轰炸那里的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.68,0:07:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马士文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.10,0:07:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想做出危害殖民地的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.19,0:07:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是那里接近中心部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.22,0:07:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打一炮也不会损及殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.31,0:07:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了死去的人们\N这是非做不可的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.01,0:07:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战争必然会带来死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.57,0:07:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,士兵们将为吉翁工国\N而捐躯成仁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.90,0:07:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必要厚丧死去的人阿\马士文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.99,0:07:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.84,0:08:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是,怎样才最能安慰他们的在天之灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.50,0:08:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.52,0:08:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还不懂吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.40,0:08:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是...是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.33,0:08:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是替他们报仇,马士文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.67,0:08:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马士文,只是挖坟墓是不够的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.12,0:08:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是军人,应该了解这点的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.23,0:08:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵从哈曼大人的命令\N是我们唯一能做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.72,0:08:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下手,下手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.49,0:08:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道...立刻发炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.74,0:08:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要怕,战斗,起来战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.71,0:08:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度,Z高达呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.27,0:08:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法马上出动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.14,0:08:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要开核战机了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.65,0:08:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇马达就留给你救\N你有办法吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.73,0:08:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要看不起人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.24,0:08:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛!\N小心点阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.98,0:08:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.81,0:09:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安多拉连我们都想干掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.19,0:09:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你发什么呆?敌人过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.29,0:09:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个不是亚加玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.50,0:09:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说给你饭吃\N要你的工作的人就是你阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.45,0:09:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男儿大志是不可轻易更改的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.58,0:09:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你...你支持亚加玛吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.55,0:09:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没有死?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.70,0:09:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.31,0:09:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚加玛在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.38,0:09:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那边..那边...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.92,0:09:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.12,0:09:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快坐上MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.67,0:09:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.46,0:09:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快上来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.21,0:09:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要驾驶Z高达回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.56,0:09:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了,信号弹还没拿回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.03,0:09:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那东西不重要!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.51,0:09:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚加玛市看信号弹行动的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.70,0:09:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了,你等一下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.67,0:09:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.38,0:09:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要打死他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.74,0:09:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了,就是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.44,0:09:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.30,0:10:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会轻易被踩死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.08,0:10:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接着!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.80,0:10:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.18,0:10:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.22,0:10:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.72,0:10:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新武器吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.33,0:10:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.33,0:10:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚加玛行动的话怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.71,0:10:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得赶快通知那是误射的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.49,0:10:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色的烟火\N是舱口打开的信号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.68,0:10:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!准备上升\N全体人员回到岗位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.39,0:10:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.75,0:10:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.97,0:10:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就负责到底\N打开舱口就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.76,0:10:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们想打开舱口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.77,0:10:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逸札,阻止他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.84,0:10:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己想啊!\N可恶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.11,0:10:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我进入舱口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.03,0:10:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能进入吗!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.03,0:11:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.49,0:11:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别管小老鼠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.35,0:11:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个小鬼跑去哪里了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.11,0:11:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好了,被刚才的炮弹给埋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.40,0:11:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那艘船太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.83,0:11:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望驾驶舱安然无恙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.77,0:11:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小子,刚才你居然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.42,0:11:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看后面!看后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.89,0:11:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雅加玛飞出来了,在右侧地区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.66,0:11:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了!糟了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.58,0:11:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出来的太早了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.45,0:12:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雅加玛...原来是躲在那里啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.42,0:12:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道有没有问题?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.65,0:12:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么问题?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.79,0:12:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是哥哥没回来怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.65,0:12:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.24,0:12:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度不是那种抛弃妹妹的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.89,0:12:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还比较担心花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.56,0:12:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她想留在香格里拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.83,0:12:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却勉强自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.94,0:12:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.89,0:12:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能源箱放自这里阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.73,0:12:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢!剩下怎办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.82,0:12:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经全部放好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.11,0:12:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,我们来大展身手\N把敌人打的落花流水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.26,0:12:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对,这样嘉美尤才...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.58,0:12:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看,客人登场了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.19,0:12:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好,继续追逐雅加玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.81,0:12:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是舱口打开的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.08,0:13:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时就发射主炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.32,0:13:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打开舱口就不会危害到市民\N正合我意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.16,0:13:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太花时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.37,0:13:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能动吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我赶上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.68,0:13:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也很没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.89,0:13:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少啰唆!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.33,0:13:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想毁灭雅加玛吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.39,0:13:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雅加玛是很值钱的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.55,0:13:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z高达?舱口打开了,他干什么回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.92,0:13:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.11,0:13:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.17,0:13:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,180度回转,向舱口前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.57,0:13:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长!是捷度,他有话要说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.73,0:14:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.64,0:14:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的信号是错误的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.38,0:14:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.33,0:14:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是误射的烟火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.92,0:14:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你休想碍事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.82,0:14:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让雅加玛出去就不值钱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.39,0:14:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停止回转!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.43,0:14:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.96,0:14:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度,引开敌人上升吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.73,0:14:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你再干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.25,0:14:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度在前面,我不能开炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.32,0:14:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.44,0:14:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,我马上赶走敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.55,0:14:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雅加玛停止改变方向了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.72,0:14:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.78,0:14:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收破烂的MS妨碍雅加玛的航行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.42,0:14:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是机会,开炮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.73,0:14:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么开炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.99,0:14:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮你调整光波威力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.51,0:15:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万一在殖民地上面开动\N我可不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.71,0:15:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盖特!你可别死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.48,0:15:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z高达\N太好了,命中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.77,0:15:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉!你是何时...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.92,0:15:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特雷斯,准备主炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.48,0:15:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必要时可能会用上\N好好牵制安多啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.03,0:15:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.08,0:15:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么震动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.84,0:15:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你总是坏我的好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.27,0:15:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿就更火大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.18,0:15:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有办法你就开枪你就开吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.91,0:15:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放手阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.54,0:15:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z高达,又是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.79,0:15:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你总是妨碍我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.32,0:15:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?这家伙的身体...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.52,0:16:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这个泰坦军人得过悲惨生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.38,0:16:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被迫在垃圾堆工作\N拍那老头的马屁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.13,0:16:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是你害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.89,0:16:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来这殖民地也是因为上次战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.37,0:16:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被你打败才这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.50,0:16:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我干的\N你还装傻!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.89,0:16:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你害我好几次差点死掉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.99,0:16:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说过不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.99,0:16:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我干的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.62,0:16:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露卡紧急连络!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.30,0:16:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度告诉我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.63,0:16:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舱口打开了\N我说舱口打开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.26,0:16:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,详情以后再说\N总之舱口打开了,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.27,0:16:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.41,0:16:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.53,0:16:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露卡...好各坚强的女孩阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.68,0:16:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始回转!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.50,0:16:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别做傻事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.67,0:16:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傻事?什么意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.34,0:16:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回转完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.06,0:16:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,前进\N不,后退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.05,0:17:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雅加玛往舱口去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.21,0:17:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.88,0:17:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在攻击会危害到殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.24,0:17:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等他们开到不会波及到\N殖民地的地方在开炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.46,0:17:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙想撞上雅加玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.34,0:17:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雅加玛,快逃,我也要逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.04,0:17:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陆卡打开舱口了!\N你要逃到哪里去?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.29,0:17:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露卡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.51,0:17:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.98,0:17:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.04,0:17:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.57,0:17:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个是必杀变身术!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.21,0:17:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.01,0:17:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,开炮!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.82,0:17:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前面有MS的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.36,0:17:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起干掉发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.65,0:18:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射激光炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.83,0:18:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.87,0:18:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主炮被...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.70,0:18:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安多拉依然接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.87,0:18:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们想在我们进入舱口攻击?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.81,0:18:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把主炮瞄准安多啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.14,0:18:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.45,0:18:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,计算距离,把安多拉击沉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.08,0:18:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主炮能源调整
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.32,0:18:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z高达,你再干什么\N让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.62,0:18:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!必须变为MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.67,0:18:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是Z高达!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.67,0:18:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我用哈玛哈玛出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.34,0:18:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.40,0:18:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然对不起死去的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.63,0:18:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈玛哈妈不能出击吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.44,0:18:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.12,0:18:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.81,0:19:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射甲板受到严重损伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.79,0:19:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.78,0:19:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈玛哈玛好还没组合好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.46,0:19:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.53,0:19:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安多拉飞离亚加码的射程距离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.86,0:19:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无法控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.50,0:19:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去...\N会对不起死去的同志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.38,0:19:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈曼大人说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.70,0:19:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必定要厚丧战死的同志们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.72,0:19:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及在战争死去的殖民地的人民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.94,0:19:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.16,0:19:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是...我是新人类!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.93,0:19:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停下来变形吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.95,0:20:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ㄟ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.30,0:20:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.91,0:20:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.71,0:20:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.01,0:20:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.48,0:20:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.42,0:20:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,担心死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.74,0:20:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.75,0:20:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干的好,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.94,0:20:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么了不起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.19,0:20:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你会打赢,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.83,0:20:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露卡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.49,0:20:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她会引导亚加玛去拉比安罗兹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.32,0:20:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要直接飞去宇宙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.17,0:20:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能破坏香格里拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.67,0:20:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还要工作还要上学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.93,0:20:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在亚加玛学习一下比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.97,0:20:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不这么认为吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.95,0:20:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长,要离开殖民地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.66,0:20:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露卡在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.71,0:20:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.15,0:21:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油阿,亚加码
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.07,0:21:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着,马士文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.13,0:21:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过去我教导你许多道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.12,0:21:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实最重要的是\N去适应地球风俗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.22,0:21:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,理解当地人与那里的习惯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.14,0:21:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样才能掌握地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.20,0:21:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈曼大人\N我该怎么做才能够理解呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.29,0:21:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马士文大人\N这是撞上安多拉的MS中找到的骨头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.45,0:21:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有一根骨头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.24,0:21:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.66,0:21:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是猪骨头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.47,0:21:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.75,0:21:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地的市民也该厚丧才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.95,0:22:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马士文大人\N下次我们一定要替同伴报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.30,0:22:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马士文大人! 马士文大人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.00,0:22:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.46,0:22:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到厚丧能这样提高士气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.84,0:22:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来这就是哈曼大人说的道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.58,0:22:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会替你们报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.84,0:22:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且一定将地球掌握在手里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.85,0:22:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有要加快组合哈玛哈玛\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.34,0:22:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着吧,亚加玛

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.10,0:22:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在没有道路的荒野里\N道もない荒れた原野に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.10,0:22:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建造铁路真是一件辛苦差事\Nレールを作るのは苦しいことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.10,0:23:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是\Nだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.50,0:23:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以不知晓远方\N遠い向こうも知らなくちゃいけない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.70,0:23:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们的路现在才开始\N僕達は これからなんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.80,0:23:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们都说我们是“忘记了梦想的小孩子”\N“夢を忘れた子供達”と 人は言う
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.50,0:23:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 时代正在哭泣\Nああー 時代が泣いている

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.81,0:23:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为只要到了广阔的宇宙就没问题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.14,0:23:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 马士文却赌上了玫瑰花 真烦人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.36,0:23:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巨大的MS悍马·悍马 很可怕 看起来很强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.08,0:23:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果我却忘记了光束步枪的弹夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.05,0:24:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么这就是拼死的作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.24,0:24:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回 高达ZZ 宇宙的捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.39,0:24:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以看到NEWTYPE的战斗场面！
